For all those who love retro music, this is a song by Mukesh ji, sung by my dad-in-law @ashim_nagpal

Purab aur Paschim  was an iconic film of the era which highlighted the dilution of  our "Sabhyata" with migration to UK..Mukesh ji  with an emotional undertone to the song created magic...which still has an everlasting appeal....Enjoy with headphones 🎧 On and embark on a journey of recreation of Retro music

Directed by @directorhimanshukanojia
